      The {{USBAlternateInterface}} object <a>this</a> belongs to.
    </td>
  </tr>  
  <tr>
    <td><dfn>\[[endpointAddress]]</dfn></td>
    <td>&lt;always set in prose></td>
    <td>
      The endpoint address of this endpoint.
